data.description:
Welcome to 2396 Blodgett, nestled in the heart of the charming Lakeside neighborhood in Muskegon! This stunning home has undergone a complete renovation, boasting 6 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms. Step inside to discover an expansive addition above the garage, providing ample space for comfortable living. Enjoy the seamless flow of the open floor plan, highlighted by a gourmet kitchen featuring custom cabinetry, quartz countertops, and top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances. The home is adorned with vinyl plank flooring throughout, complemented by plush new carpeting in the hallways and bedrooms. Outside, a detached 2-stall garage with a workshop leanto awaits, along with a Tuff Shed for additional storage. Relax and entertain in style with a new white vinyl fence enclosing the yard, complete with an above-ground pool and play equipment.

Lakeside living offers unparalleled amenities, including access to the revitalized downtown area, nearby bike paths, and a convenient boat launch for Muskegon Lake enthusiasts. Indulge in local dining and entertainment options, with McCraft Park just a stone's throw away. This home boasts numerous updates, including a high-efficiency Goodman furnace, central air, and a 40-gallon water heater. Recent additions include two bedrooms, a bathroom, and a new roof, all completed in 2020. Other notable upgrades include a Tuff Shed, fence, sewer pipe with cleanouts, and new windows installed in 2020. Plus, enjoy peace of mind with a hardwired camera system, 24/7 alarm monitoring, and garage upgrades including insulation, heating, and a floor drain.
With meticulous attention to detail and modern conveniences throughout, 2396 Blodgett offers the perfect blend of comfort and sophistication. Don't miss your opportunity to call this exquisite Lakeside property home!
